Question.Subject: how to remove this error that's skype IE plugin error?
Question.Content: hai, frequently, getting message skype ie plugin error in my IE web-browser.what is the error? and how to remove this error .
Question.ChosenAnswer:
firstly i would like to suggest you that IE is worst web browser....use any othr browser like MOZILLA,SAFARI,OPERA,CHROME etc.
but you can solve your Problem by following steps: open IE then press alt key then T then select Internet Option.. then Select Advance then select REST or RESTORE options.
if nothing works then install plugins from adobe.com u can also find easily from google search (IE plugins)...
try it!!
